<section>
	<h2>Mission</h2>
	<p>We are not delusional about technology being a magical thing who will fulfill &amp; liberate humanity.</p>
	<p>That’s why we are focusing on <strong>web quality</strong>, <strong>accessibility</strong>, <strong>privacy</strong> and <strong>maintainability</strong> to deliver the more <strong>ethical</strong> human-sized projects possible.<br>
	We do what we think is right and without bullshit.</p>
	<p>Along with that we’re helping other organizations embracing those values one radical step at a time.</p>
	<p>And some times we just do projects for fun!</p>
</section>
